= Comment Blocks

Comment blocks allow you to add notes that won't appear in the rendered output.

== Single Line Comments

// This is a single line comment that won't be rendered.

This paragraph will be visible.

// Another single line comment.

== Multi-line Comment Blocks

////
This is a multi-line comment block.
It can span multiple lines.

And paragraphs.

It won't appear in the output.
////

This content will be visible.

////
Another comment block.
////

== Comments Around Content

// Comment before paragraph

This paragraph is visible.

// Comment after paragraph

== Comments in Lists

* First item // inline comment
* Second item
// Comment between items
* Third item

== Comments with Code

[source]
----
code here
----

// Comment about the code above

== Comments with Blocks

////
Comment before block
////

====
Example block content
====

////
Comment after block
////

